classDiagram
direction LR

class AgentController {
  +POST /api/agents/register()
  +POST /api/agents/heartbeat()
}

class PortalController {
  +GET /api/overview()
  +GET /api/nodes()
  +GET /api/nodes/{id}()
  +GET /api/services()
  +GET /api/services/{id}()
  +GET /api/trends()
  +GET /api/tracing/summary()
}

class NodeRegistryService {
  +registerNode()
  +heartbeat()
  +overview()
  +listNodes()
  +getNode()
  +listServices()
  +getService()
  +getTrends()
  +saveMetricsSnapshot()
}

class SkyWalkingQueryService {
  +loadTracingSummary()
  +loadLatestTracePreview()
}

class ManagedNode {
  +Long id
  +String nodeName
  +String hostname
  +String ipAddress
  +String osName
  +String agentVersion
  +String status
  +Instant lastSeenAt
  +Instant lastHeartbeatAt
}

class DiscoveredService {
  +Long id
  +String serviceName
  +String serviceType
  +Integer port
  +String processName
  +String metricsPath
  +Integer metricsPort
}

class NodeMetrics {
  +Long id
  +Instant collectedAt
  +Double cpuUsage
  +Double memoryUsage
  +Double diskUsage
  +Double networkRxMbps
  +Double networkTxMbps
}

class HeartbeatEvent {
  +Long id
  +String status
  +Instant createdAt
}

class MetricsSnapshot {
  +Long id
  +Instant timestamp
  +long totalNodes
  +long onlineNodes
  +long warningNodes
  +long totalServices
  +long abnormalServices
  +long unresolvedAlerts
}

AgentController --> NodeRegistryService : 写入注册/心跳
PortalController --> NodeRegistryService : 读取聚合结果
PortalController --> SkyWalkingQueryService : 读取 Trace 摘要

ManagedNode "1" --> "*" DiscoveredService : services
ManagedNode "1" --> "*" NodeMetrics : metrics
ManagedNode "1" --> "*" HeartbeatEvent : events

NodeRegistryService --> ManagedNode : 管理节点主数据
NodeRegistryService --> DiscoveredService : 同步服务目录
NodeRegistryService --> NodeMetrics : 保存资源采样
NodeRegistryService --> HeartbeatEvent : 记录状态历史
NodeRegistryService --> MetricsSnapshot : 保存趋势快照

note for NodeRegistryService "负责状态归一化、异常判定、快捷链接生成和趋势聚合"
note for SkyWalkingQueryService "通过 GraphQL 查询 SkyWalking OAP\n过滤业务 Trace 并生成结构化摘要"
